name: Boy hugging Bear - art print
description:
This illustration is part of the 'Grubbies' series by Grubby Princess. Sweet 8x10" vintage-inspired art print. This is a simple, understated artwork in muted tones, featuring a boy hugging his favourite teddy bear. Perfect for hanging in any little boys room or nursery.

This illustration was hand-drawn with ink, and then digitally coloured. It has been printed onto 170gsm matte photo paper, signed by the artist and will be shipped to you with care and ready for framing. 
--------------------------- 
PLEASE NOTE: 
Frames are not included. 
Color may vary slightly from what is viewed on your computer monitor.

description:

This is the original Grubby Princess, the one who started it all! This little character was originally inspired by daughter, but I am sure we all know a 'Grubby Princess' or two!

Grubby Princess is a little girl who loves to have fun, she laughs everyday, makes friends wherever she goes and has amazing adventures. Grubby Princess is smart and brave and pretty and fun and kind. But oh boy was she GRUBBY!
